<!-- templates/urgent-expiry-reminder.hbs -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>紧急：会员即将到期</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.02); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .urgent-notice {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border: 2px solid #f5c6cb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .countdown {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .btn-urgent {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 18px 35px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            animation: glow 2s infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes glow {
            from { box-shadow: 0 0 10px #dc3545; }
            to { box-shadow: 0 0 20px #dc3545, 0 0 30px #dc3545; }
        }
        .content {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-top: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🚨 紧急提醒</h1>
        <p>您的会员即将到期</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="urgent-notice">
            <h2>⏰ 倒计时</h2>
            <div class="countdown">{{remainingHours}} 小时</div>
            <p>您的 <strong>{{planName}}</strong> 将在 {{remainingHours}} 小时后到期！</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>亲爱的用户，</p>
        <p>这是最后的提醒！您的会员服务即将在 <strong>{{endDate}}</strong> 到期。</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{renewUrl}}" class="btn-urgent">🔥 紧急续费</a>
        </div>
        
        <h3>⚠️ 到期后将失去的功能：</h3>
        <ul style="color: #dc3545;">
            <li>❌ 多平台内容发布功能</li>
            <li>❌ 消息聚合服务</li>
            <li>❌ 优先客服支持</li>
            <li>❌ 高级数据分析</li>
        </ul>
        
        <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4 style="color: #155724; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">💡 温馨提示</h4>
            <p style="color: #155724; margin: 0;">现在续费，您的会员时间将在当前到期时间基础上延长，不会浪费剩余时间！</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>如需帮助，请立即联系我们：</p>
        <p>📞 客服热线：400-xxx-xxxx</p>
        <p>💬 在线客服：<a href="{{contactUrl}}">点击联系</a></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿回复</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
